Package: erlang-toml
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, erlang-base
Description: TOML parser for Erlang
 toml is an Erlang library application for parsing TOML configuration
 language. It supports parsing 0.4.0 version of the TOML specification.

Package: erlang-toml-doc
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: TOML parser for Erlang - API documentation
 toml is an Erlang library application for parsing TOML configuration
 language. It supports parsing 0.4.0 version of the TOML specification.
 .
 This package contains API documentation generated from sources.
